race.comment: VANDEVELDE (6) just missed the placings at the Sunny Coast when facing the starter for the first time and will have derived a stack of benefit from that race day experience. Doesn't need to improve much to be fighting out the finish in this. The well-related POWER REECE (8) (half to 3xListed winner Snitzkraft) was well in the betting on debut but didn't measure up in town on that occasion. Has since tuned up for this with a recent trial win and is sure to be up to the mark out of the Gollan barn. Watch for sharp improvement. NOTTINGTON PRINCE (3) has placed three from four over this distance range and will strip fitter second-up from the break. Top-three aspirations. BOOMTOWN LADDIE (1) has been thereabouts in both starts to date and only needs some luck navigating from the outside draw to be featuring in the finish. SKINNY JEANS (9) best of the rest.
